## What you need to modify

Your project has 12 files. You only need to care about 4:

| File | What it does | When to edit |
|------|-------------|-------------|
| `app/pages/` | File-based route pages | **Every time** |
| `app/components/` | Vue components | **Every time** |
| `server/api/` | API route handlers | **Every time** |
| `tests/` | Tests for components and pages | **Every time** |
| Others (nuxt.config.ts, ESLint) | Project infra | Almost never |

